product_desc:
New-Age designs will be providing numerous design services to other companies in need of advertisements in Nairobi area and other regions in Kenya, and later going international. The company’s public retail outlet will focus on providing the necessary material selections that will bring customers into the company.
New-Age designs will have the following services:
•	Graphics Designs;
•	3D Animations;
•	Video Shooting;
•	Interior Designs and Constructions;
•	Advertisements;
•	Web Designing.
